{"tid":1705420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日要多謝一眾前線的手足","createTime":"2019-11-11T01:23:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T02:03:57.000Z","uid":50457,"like":66,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fb7490edb6671c5847c3fc63bb7aa9df72989445","tid":1705420,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T01:23:00.000Z","msg":"今日損失好大，但開始動搖到香港人罷工的決心，第一次出現罷工破窗效應<br />\n<br />\n當大家慢慢試過一日，兩日，三日被迫返唔到工，公司就會開始制訂政策，間接下一次真罷工提供心理基礎<br />\n<br />\n罷工尤如十號風球打風，停一日半日，世界只會繼續轉，影響並沒有大家想像咁大，重點係要有大部份人覺醒，咁樣大家就安全。<br />\n<br />\n在香港危難中，非常感謝奮不顧身，為香港犧牲的手足。在此，香港人對所有手足都會不離不棄，終身支持每一個手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n面對漫罵不退縮<br />\n面對死亡不畏懼<br />\n敢於為公義發聲<br />\n敢於為良知犧牲<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b575adefe454dcf6590f93945415db84ac78fee0","tid":1705420,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T01:30:04.000Z","msg":"我用最卑微嘅心，求吓你哋<br />\n<br />\n香港人，忍無可忍！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1705050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1705050</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6b06faefd643f14b6d027601c60c524b0954f800","tid":1705420,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-1